data.description: Become the owner of one of the LIMITED 5-bedroom residences in the charming Breakfast Point neighborhood. Crafted by Samuel Taylor, this home boasts an inviting open-concept design in the main living area, ensuring ample space and privacy when needed. One bedroom is situated at the front of the house, while three more are located in a separate section, with the master suite in a distinct area off the backyard.
